data.description: The 2 story foyer opens to a study or living room on the right with the formal dining room next!  The kitchen, nook and family room are spaciously open with the enjoyment of the fireplace evident to each room. The kitchen boasts granite counter tops and stainless appliances.    If you have never had enough closet space - my of my- this is for you!  The master suite has his and her walk in closets!!  The downstairs is beautiful hardwood laminate gracefully gliding from foyer to family room!.  The front has a  large covered porch for entry and the rear has a covered entertaining patio.  Suzy with Movement Mortgage is the preferred lender with a $2000.00 incentive for the buyer's use.
